	(text_box "3V3 will be fed into the ADC after we loaded the input in. \nSequence:\n1. Sample - Set TMUX1104 to the sensor input, all TMUX1133 bits to VSMP, and close TOP_RESET switch (top plate will have 1.65V ref on it now).\n2. Trap - OPEN the TOP_RESET switch via SR2-QG. This traps the charge on the top plate before any voltages change.\n3. Swap - Switch TMUX1104 to the 3.3V reference and flip all bit switches to GND.\n4. Search - Execute the binary search from Bit 13 down to 0."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 26.67 46.99 0)
		(size 100.33 19.05)
		(margins 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525)
		(stroke
			(width 0)
			(type solid)
		)
		(fill
			(type color)
			(color 0 0 255 0.1)
		)
		(effects
